Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.79,0:00:08.52,Default,Thugs,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:11.44,Default,Thugs,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.75,0:00:14.90,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.38,0:00:16.70,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.78,0:00:33.26,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Gouda Takeo, a first-year in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.08,0:00:36.26,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,For the very first time in my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.26,0:00:39.01,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,a girl I like actually likes me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.55,0:00:42.02,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,She's my first girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:47.90,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:50.40,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.12,0:00:52.15,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I love her!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.45,0:00:56.20,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Um, it's the first time I've seen \Nyou on the morning train.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.20,0:00:58.69,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Do you always take this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.69,0:00:59.52,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.81,0:01:02.16,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll switch to this one, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:05.48,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But this would be cutting it close.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.77,0:01:08.18,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to be on the same train,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.18,0:01:09.54,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,but I shouldn't be late to class, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.99,0:01:11.12,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.12,0:01:13.17,Default,Students,0000,0000,0000,,That couple there is pretty amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.40,0:01:14.46,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I shouldn't, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:15.35,Default,Students,0000,0000,0000,,No way, they must be father and daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.87,0:01:17.18,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I shouldn't be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:17.72,Default,Students,0000,0000,0000,,But that man's in a school uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:57.61,Class,Sign 0258,0000,0000,0000,,Class 1-6
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:04.91,Title1,Sign 0302,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Dense
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:06.33,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,We'll pick up where we left off \Nyesterday, on page 24.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:08.37,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Kurihara-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.94,0:03:10.25,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:12.17,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.44,0:03:16.75,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,All right, page 24, people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.28,0:03:20.72,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,I already got to see a good show today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:27.52,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing it revved me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:29.98,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,I'd have gone for a first \Nkiss right there and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:31.39,Default,Kaki,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo'd never do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:32.60,Default,Fudo,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:34.94,Default,100,0000,0000,0000,,Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:36.62,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,But afterward...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.62,0:03:39.09,Default - italics,Train,0000,0000,0000,,Please mind the closing doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.27,0:03:42.02,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm getting off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:43.53,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:45.78,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.29,0:03:47.21,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:49.60,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:54.24,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo missed his transfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:02.42,SignA,Sign 0402,0000,0000,0000,,Great. \N\NIt's amazing!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:10.76,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,He was so cool, I couldn't \Nresist taking a video.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.76,0:04:11.97,Default,100,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.97,0:04:13.18,Default,Fudo,0000,0000,0000,,It was a limited express, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:14.73,SFX-BlackWhite,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14}{\an9}So cool
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:15.09,Default,Kaki,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo must've gone all the \Nway to the final stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:17.23,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,But why did she pick Gouda-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:18.93,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she's cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.93,0:04:19.69,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:20.99,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:22.74,SignB,Sign 0422,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a Koizumi Girls' Academy uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:23.24,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:25.09,SignB,Sign 0423,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a Koizumi Girls' Academy uniform? \N\NAre they really going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:25.92,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, starting at page 24.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:25.99,SignB,Sign 0426,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a Koizumi Girls' Academy uniform? \N\NAre they really going out? \N\NNo way (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:28.49,SignB,Sign 0427,0000,0000,0000,,Are they really going out? \N\NNo way (lol) \N\NNo normal girl'd like Gouda-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:28.74,SignB,,0000,0000,0000,,No normal girl'd like Gouda-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:46.51,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:49.11,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know it was possible \Nto take such nice videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.02,0:04:51.27,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:53.32,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Can I see it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.32,0:04:54.14,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:54.90,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:56.14,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,How do you work this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:56.89,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:05.32,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Someone, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:06.45,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,My boy fell into the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:07.24,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Someone, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:10.37,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:37.52,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:39.68,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Take him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:44.58,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, I was scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.58,0:05:45.64,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:47.35,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.76,0:05:49.03,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:51.83,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:54.34,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't me. He saved your boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.34,0:05:56.31,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna, let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:58.43,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm running late to my date!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:05:59.85,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:01.50,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You're dripping wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:02.84,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:05.20,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.78,0:06:07.23,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You're some superhuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:12.81,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:14.31,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.79,0:06:16.31,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:21.27,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:24.99,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You're drenched, but it isn't raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.99,0:06:27.55,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,On his way here, he saved a drowning boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:28.70,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:32.12,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sunakawa-kun, you're pretty dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:33.91,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I only handed the boy to his mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:36.29,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who jumped in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:39.28,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You jumped in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.28,0:06:40.34,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:41.67,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You jumped in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:45.28,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I love her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:49.87,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I have a towel, but it's hardly big enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:52.18,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You should have gone home to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:55.18,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:07:00.19,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You could have called or texted her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:02.72,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:04.16,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,you're so smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.16,0:07:07.19,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking that, too. \NYou're really smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:08.69,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I have gym clothes. Want them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:09.86,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:11.03,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:19.25,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:21.29,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:22.67,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I guess girlfriends
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:26.29,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,call or text you, even when \Nthere's no real reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.29,0:07:28.92,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I made a roll cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.33,0:07:33.38,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,A friend asked me to make some for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.38,0:07:34.93,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm not sure how good it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:38.17,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This one has whole strawberries in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.05,0:07:41.86,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,And they bake you cakes, even when \Nit isn't your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:40.56,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}and I tried adding banana to \Nthe batter for this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:45.08,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.08,0:07:46.33,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:50.04,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You always say everything's \Ndelicious, Takeo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:51.82,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious, right, Suna?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:52.45,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:54.66,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a small thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.52,0:07:59.16,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,but she laughs like hearing \Nit makes her really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:09.00,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:17.77,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,There was a bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:20.58,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I already got rid of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:21.55,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:27.36,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry for touching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:29.32,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.99,0:08:32.21,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier, she was blushing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.82,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,She's really pure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:37.37,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,She's the total opposite of my mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:39.58,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,who was once an amateur wrestler.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:42.58,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get going, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.81,0:08:44.51,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:48.44,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you wash that before you return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:51.09,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,That was subtle, giving us a moment alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:53.51,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,What a considerate guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:56.89,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun, do you want \Nto go through the park?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.78,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a detour?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:01.77,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You get a really great view of the stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:06.78,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:08.08,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,They're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:10.27,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's dark, so you can see them really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:17.66,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't anyone around here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:19.78,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:27.46,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's just the two of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:41.59,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.59,0:09:42.14,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:44.87,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Until you're all grown up,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:47.29,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I won't touch a single hair on your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:48.33,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,So don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.01,0:09:54.49,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:09:58.15,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.15,0:09:59.31,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Good night...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.42,0:10:05.04,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treat her right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:12.54,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do everything in my \Npower to treat her right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:14.89,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Today was a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:20.76,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:22.30,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Makoto, welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:26.14,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're back, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:28.44,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I took the afternoon bullet train.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:29.98,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Here's my present.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:31.11,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Takeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:32.37,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:34.50,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot in there. \NWhy not share with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:35.23,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,You can call him over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.77,0:10:37.92,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,He's walking his girlfriend home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.13,0:10:41.64,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo has a girlfriend now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:42.26,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:43.50,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo has a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.50,0:10:44.16,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.47,0:10:46.30,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:47.68,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pull my leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:49.29,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:50.29,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,She's pretty cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.33,0:10:57.00,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.11,0:10:59.58,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:01.05,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:05.06,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute... Don't tell me \Nyou had feelings for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.09,0:11:07.81,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:09.73,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:10.29,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Since when?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.93,0:11:12.98,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,What's she like?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:15.96,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure he isn't being duped?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:17.36,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,He's so trusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:20.37,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way Takeo would get a girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.37,0:11:23.04,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Not a big, lumbering gorilla like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.04,0:11:25.12,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,So do you like him or hate him? Which?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:26.77,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure he isn't being used?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:29.14,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Like, for a bodyguard?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.14,0:11:31.51,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,He looks happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.51,0:11:34.13,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen two people \Ngenuinely in love before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:39.66,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Let me meet this girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:42.52,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Only a woman would understand \Nanother woman's true nature!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:43.82,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:46.93,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible that any girl other than \Nme would have feelings for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:47.80,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,There's got to be something going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:49.73,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Let me meet Takeo's girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:51.20,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,No, I smell a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.20,0:11:53.02,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,What? Let me see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:55.15,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo's still his lame self, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:57.10,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,He still has his weird \Nhairstyle, doesn't he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:11:58.31,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really even actually like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:12:00.23,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, gimme your cell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.23,0:12:01.90,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:16.13,SignC,Sign 1207,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,3565)}To: Takeo-kun \NSubject: Um \N\NUm, Takeo-kun. \NI have something I want to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:16.13,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't tell you this until now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:17.82,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:25.01,SignD,Sign 1225,0000,0000,0000,,Cancel \N{\c&H87807A&}Discard changes? \NCancel    OK
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:29.52,SignC,Sign 1226,0000,0000,0000,,To: Takeo-kun \NSubject: Hello \N\NTakeo-kun, \Ntoday was really fun. \NWhen can I see you again? \NI'll bake cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:37.90,SignD,Sign 1237,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Subject: Re: Hello \N\NI'm free Wednesday. \NI had fun, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:46.99,EyecatchA - Copy,,0000,0000,0000,,Love
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:47.99,EyecatchB - Copy,,0000,0000,0000,,Sincerity
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:51.72,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's about time you \Nstopped having me tag along?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:55.00,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato seems like a very pure-hearted person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.39,0:12:57.76,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,When it's just the two of us, \NI think she gets nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:00.50,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,If you're there, she'll be more relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:02.01,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:12.93,Default - italics,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,So, who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:14.78,Default - italics,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,That one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:16.81,Default - italics,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,This one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.39,0:13:18.95,Default - italics,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.95,0:13:20.12,Default - italics,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,No, she can't be the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.12,0:13:22.24,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Takeo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:23.69,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.16,0:13:26.45,Default - italics,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.94,0:13:28.32,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:30.32,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,No, I haven't been waiting at all—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:31.40,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:35.07,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.80,0:13:37.64,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.64,0:13:39.79,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you have a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.33,0:13:42.84,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,GPS...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.78,0:13:45.61,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's Suna's big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:47.43,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:49.47,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yamato. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:52.22,SFX-BlueWhite,Sign 1351,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\c&H8D9F86&}Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:54.80,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,She's pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:55.77,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.57,0:13:59.00,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna's sister is good-looking,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:00.52,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,so as a kid, I used to get nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:04.34,Default - flashback,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get your homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:05.62,Default - flashback,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:06.82,Default - flashback,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:08.53,Default - flashback,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Your pants are on backwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.44,0:14:10.27,Default - flashback,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.27,0:14:11.40,Default - flashback,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,your nose is dripping.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:13.07,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,And just like Suna,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.07,0:14:14.98,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,at heart, she's a kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.59,0:14:18.67,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yamato-san. \NWhat do you like about Takeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:19.90,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:21.63,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.79,0:14:25.64,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:28.39,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to explain,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.39,0:14:30.93,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,but I really like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:34.70,Default - italics,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Hard to explain, but likes him just the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.73,0:14:38.31,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1437,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(103,1)}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.82,0:14:38.31,Default - italics,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:41.48,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I baked cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:43.44,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like some, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:44.57,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Only if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:50.31,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, they're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.31,0:14:52.82,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,You made these cookies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:14:57.55,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,They're really well-made.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:14:59.62,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, I'm really into icings,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:01.95,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,so I used icing on langues \Nde chat-type cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.53,0:15:04.59,SFX-BlueWhite,Sign 1503,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(103,1)}Langues de chat-type?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:07.44,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato's really good at baking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:09.16,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Her cakes are great, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.29,0:15:11.95,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like she's a girly girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:12.90,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.90,0:15:14.91,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato is a girly girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:15.85,SFX-BlueWhite,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}{\fad(112,1)}Okay, okay
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:17.98,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,She's a nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.82,0:15:19.73,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,She's a very nice person!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:21.54,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't true!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:23.18,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a good person at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.18,0:15:24.75,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be modest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:25.94,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.67,0:15:34.83,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Digging in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.82,0:15:37.15,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,It's salty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:42.02,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see, it's savory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.02,0:15:42.83,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:45.67,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,This is new...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:48.26,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's salty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:50.80,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:54.55,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I mixed up the sugar and salt!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:56.56,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.56,0:15:58.24,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Takeo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:15:59.32,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't eat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.32,0:16:01.93,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my god! I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.93,0:16:03.35,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:08.53,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:10.46,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I want to eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:12.24,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Give them all to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:17.24,SFX-BlueWhite,Sign 1616,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\c&HE66CEB&}*Blush*
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:27.41,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I like sweet things and super salty things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.41,0:16:28.59,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:31.17,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, is there anything you don't like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.81,0:16:32.93,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:42.18,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Then what do you like \Nabout Yamato-san, Takeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:45.95,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh, my god! That's so sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:46.09,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, everything, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:47.19,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,but if I had to choose...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.89,0:16:50.94,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,She's pure-hearted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:03.36,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll walk Yamato home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:04.92,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:06.25,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Night!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.72,0:17:08.54,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:10.00,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,They look happy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.41,0:17:13.41,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,She has a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:16.88,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you overthinking this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.88,0:17:19.61,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.61,0:17:22.52,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,She's hiding something from Takeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:28.27,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't been totally honest \Nabout herself with Takeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:31.78,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's two-timing \Nhim or having an affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:36.15,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,She has something she \Ndoesn't want to tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:37.26,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:40.43,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:42.79,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The stars look great today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:46.54,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.84,0:17:50.54,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,They cheer you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.69,0:18:03.01,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:07.56,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:12.07,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:19.07,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm dense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:20.98,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:22.18,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.18,0:18:22.83,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:28.08,SFX-BlueWhite,Sign 1826,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.49,0:18:26.55,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:38.76,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:41.72,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:45.43,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:55.24,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yamato?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:19:02.83,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,When she said she'd fallen for Takeo at first sight, \Nyou should've known something was off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:04.82,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,She wouldn't have fallen in love with him
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.82,0:19:07.24,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,unless she had a real reason to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.24,0:19:10.85,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I bet she's hiding a big secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:14.14,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.14,0:19:15.77,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I need some space.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:18.41,Default,SMom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.41,0:19:20.44,Default,SMom,0000,0000,0000,,Ai, can you go shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:21.41,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.41,0:19:23.78,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Your daughter hasn't been home for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.78,0:19:25.76,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,and you're already abusing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:28.48,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:44.72,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, it's creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.72,0:19:47.00,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,This is seriously scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:48.25,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,It's hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.55,0:19:53.67,Default - italics,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.89,0:19:57.61,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:20:00.23,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:02.57,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm learning about how girls think.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:03.68,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.21,0:20:06.93,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm probably dense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.61,0:20:11.74,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'd thought that Yamato \Nhad feelings for Suna.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.43,0:20:14.50,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,So I can't read girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:16.30,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,If Yamato won't tell me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.30,0:20:18.74,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I won't have a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.74,0:20:20.94,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,If only she'd tell me, I could help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.81,0:20:25.95,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,It might be something she can't tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.77,0:20:30.00,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Something she can't tell her boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:33.78,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,It could be that she's two-timing you, \Nhaving an affair,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.78,0:20:36.00,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,or that she's found someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:40.96,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that's the case, I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.78,0:20:44.97,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's more important to me that \NYamato's in knots about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.23,0:20:52.28,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I can ask her...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.26,0:20:56.45,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,It might be easier for her \Nto talk to another girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.45,0:20:57.76,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You'd do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:20:59.65,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,So stop reading those!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:01.50,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,You're creeping people out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.50,0:21:02.93,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.93,0:21:04.92,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're a nice person!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:06.78,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:12.22,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I did wonder if a guy reading \Nthat stuff might be creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.22,0:21:13.79,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,But you still read them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:16.42,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I was desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:18.18,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Did it help you figure anything out?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.18,0:21:21.10,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, not at all.
